{"id":534125,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/07/林祖恋家人发声明-拒绝认可官派律师/","date":"2016-07-05T07:52:54Z","modified":"2016-07-05T07:52:54Z","title":"林祖恋家人发声明 拒绝认可官派律师","content":"<blockquote><p>iyouport ‏<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iyouport_news/status/750209644081983488\" target=\"_blank\">@iyouport_news</a>: #乌坎 林祖恋家人发出声明，不承认当局指派的律师</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/CmlHsJjUMAAsazQ.jpg_large.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-534127\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/CmlHsJjUMAAsazQ.jpg_large.jpg\" alt=\"CmlHsJjUMAAsazQ.jpg_large\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/CmlHsJjUMAAsazQ.jpg_large.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/CmlHsJjUMAAsazQ.jpg_large-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/1786822605\" target=\"_blank\">@李方平律师</a> :【葛永喜律师：原来是王会长抢了我的业务，我只能表示服了】林祖恋孙子林立义：“你们是律师界的耻辱”这两名辩护律师是当局指派，他们分别是广州金鹏律师 事务所的王波和广东宏进律师事务所的方振宏。<br />\n王波是广州市政府法律顾问，兼任广东省律师协会副会长，从事刑事及民商事法律辩护，曾多次为被控受贿的政府官员辩护；方振宏是汕尾市人大代表和汕尾市政府法律顾问，熟悉产权及经济纠纷类案件。<br />\n下图: 广州市市长陈建华向广州金鹏律师事务所王波主任颁发广州市政府法律咨询专家聘书。<br />\n不允许家属聘律师，当局却在家属毫不知情的情况下，指定这么高大上的律师<img title=\"[弱]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d8/sad_org.gif\" alt=\"[弱]\" /><img title=\"[弱]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d8/sad_org.gif\" alt=\"[弱]\" /><img title=\"[弱]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d8/sad_org.gif\" alt=\"[弱]\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/6a80bfcdgw1f5ito2py6vj20fz0anmyd.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-534126\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/6a80bfcdgw1f5ito2py6vj20fz0anmyd.jpg\" alt=\"6a80bfcdgw1f5ito2py6vj20fz0anmyd\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/6a80bfcdgw1f5ito2py6vj20fz0anmyd.jpg 575w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/6a80bfcdgw1f5ito2py6vj20fz0anmyd-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>方振宏（党徽下红衣男子）为汕尾市“法治讲堂”进村（社）活动主讲人：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_534129\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/方振宏.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-534129\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/方振宏.jpg\" alt=\"方振宏\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/方振宏.jpg 700w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/方振宏-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">图片来源：<a style=\"color: #808080;\" href=\"http://www.swcqpfw.gov.cn/4926.html\" target=\"_blank\">汕尾市城区普法网</a></span></p></div>\n<p>“爆料”林祖恋已聘请律师的是新浪微博用户 @在城央雨飞扬，这是当时该用户账号内唯一一条微博内容：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_534149\" style=\"width: 485px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/在城央雨飞扬.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-534149\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/在城央雨飞扬.jpg\" alt=\"在城央雨飞扬\" width=\"475\" height=\"611\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/在城央雨飞扬.jpg 1812w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/在城央雨飞扬-233x300.jpg 233w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/在城央雨飞扬-768x987.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/在城央雨飞扬-797x1024.jpg 797w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@在城央雨飞扬 相关微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>腾讯网后转发了相关内容，目前已404（<a href=\"https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:SYo5tCbFc0gJ:https://view.inews.qq.com/a/NEW2016063003803203%3Fopenid%3Do04IBAFRf3O4Dkt6dJMtBfH_ZV6Y%26key%3D%26version%3D62010025%26devicetype%3DWindows%2B7%26from%3Dsingl